HEADWORD: Stonehenge
<hw>Stone"henge</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An assemblage of
upright stones with others placed horizontally on their tops, on
Salisbury Plain, England, -- generally supposed to be the remains of an
ancient Druidical temple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

